      "end": 33.959999084472656,
      "text": "Dark heart, dark star, long dead No way for me to take it away from my mind",
      "start": 26.579999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 40,
      "text": "Been down to the barrel of the mellows Found the darkness in my friend, man, don't",
